{"id":68709,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/05/纽约时报：中国高涨的能源使用威胁到了要控制全/","date":"2010-05-09T13:20:05Z","modified":"2010-05-09T13:20:05Z","title":"纽约时报：中国高涨的能源使用威胁到了要控制全球变暖的目标","content":"<h1><b><span style=\"font-size:large\">原文：<a href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2010/05/07/business/energy-environment/07energy.html?pagewanted=all\">China’s Soaring Energy Use Weakens Pledge on Efficiency &#8211; NYTimes.com</a></span></b></h1>\n<p><b><span style=\"font-size:large\">译文：<span>纽约时报：中国高涨的能源使用威胁到了要控制全球变暖的目</span><span>标</span></span></b></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:small\"><span style=\"font-family:verdana\">作者： </span><a href=\"http://topics.nytimes.com/top/reference/timestopics/people/b/keith_bradsher/index.html?inline=nyt-per\" style=\"font-family:Verdana\">KEITH BRADSHER</a><br style=\"font-family:Verdana\"><span style=\"font-family:verdana\">发布时间： May 6, 2010</span><br style=\"font-family:Verdana\"><span style=\"font-family:verdana\">译者：</span></span><span style=\"font-family:verdana;font-size:small\">leros</span><span style=\"font-family:verdana;font-size:small\"> (@leros7)</span><br />校对：@xiaomi2020</p>\n<div style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" height=\"330\" src=\"http://graphics8.nytimes.com/images/2010/05/07/business/07energy_CA0/07energy_CA0-articleLarge-v2.jpg\" width=\"600\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:x-small\">摄影：Adrian Bradshaw/欧洲图片社</span></b></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:x-small\">一名工人在铁路上卸煤。中国对电煤的需求激增</span></b></div>\n<p><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">香港</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\"> &#8211;</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\"> 中国为</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">自己设定了雄心勃勃的清洁能源生产和温室气体减排</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">目标，</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">却因为对石油和煤炭能源的强劲需求</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">，</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">引起了</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\">六</span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">个月来</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">人为温室气体</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">的最大增长，这一排放量就单一国家而言前所未有</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">。</span></span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://docs.google.com/File?id=dg5pc3d3_1493f39t2j4c_b\" style=\"float:left;height:219.569px;margin-left:0pt;margin-right:1em;width:320px\"><b><span style=\"font-size:x-small\">摄影：Sheng Li/路透社<br />图：对钢材这样的重工业的倾向已经刺激了能源需求的上扬</span></b></p>\n<p><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">中国的领导人非常关注能源利用的增加和能效的下降，</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">根据工业与信息</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">化</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">部周四</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">的一份声明，</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">国务院本周召开了一次特别会议来到讨论这个问题</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">（译注：指</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">5</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">月</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">5</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">号召开的</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">全国节能减排工作电视电话会议</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">）</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">。</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">煤、电和石油销售</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">在第一年分别同比上涨了</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">24%</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">，延续了去年第四季度的增长趋势。</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">根据上述声明，</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">为</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">加强能源节约，</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">温家宝总理允诺</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">实施更严厉的政策，包括</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">禁止政府对没有消除低效产能</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">的公司的新项目进行审批。</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">温总理</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">还指出，中国必须找出办法来实现</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">在这个五年计划内</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">提升<span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">20%</span></span>能源利用率</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">的目标。</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">“</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">无论面临多大的困难，我们的承诺不能改变，决心不能动摇，工作不能减</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">弱</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">”，温总理强调</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">。尽管西方的专家认为实现这个目标很困难，但中国的领导人</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">好像很坚定。</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">巴黎的</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">国际能源署中国项目</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">经理</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">Jonathan Sinton</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">指出： </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">“</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">就绝对量而言，</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">以前</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">没有哪个</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">这种规模的</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">国家</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">，对能源的需求增长</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">如此之快</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">，对这个问题最担忧的还是中国人自己</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">”</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">自</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">2006</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">年伊始，中国每年都</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">是世界上最大的温室气体排放国，美国紧随其后，但二者的差距与日俱增</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">。如果中国不能实现自己的能效目标，这对国际社会减排</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">的</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">努力将成为巨大的</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">阻碍。</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">这也会让中国政府面临外交上的</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">可能出现的</span><span style=\"font-size:small\">难堪局面，因为就在</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">去年</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">12</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">月</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">哥本哈根气候峰会</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">之前，中国政府向世界承诺要改进能耗。</span></span></p>\n<div style=\"margin:5pt 0pt\"><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">这个问题</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">对中国和全球能源市场都有</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">重大经济意义。</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">中国的经济基础正在从</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">出口型轻工业</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">，比如服装和鞋</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">类</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">，转向</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">能源密集型重工业，</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">例如钢铁和水泥制造业，以满足国内市场对汽车和建筑业的需求。</span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin:5pt 0pt\"></div>\n<p><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">根据政府的统计数字，</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">现在</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">几乎所有的城市家庭都拥有一台洗衣机、一个冰箱、一部</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">空调。</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">自</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">2008</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">年底政府实行补贴以来，农村地区的家电拥有量正在飙升。</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">城市里的汽车拥有量正快速攀升，而</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">在</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">农村地区</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">，由于更多的家庭购买了摩托车和轻型卡车，自行车拥有量事实上下降了。</span></span></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://topics.nytimes.com/top/news/business/companies/general_motors_corporation/index.html?inline=nyt-org\"><span><span style=\"color:blue\"><u><span style=\"font-size:small\">通用汽车</span></u></span></span></a><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">周四宣布</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">，它在中国四月份的销量同比上升了</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">41%</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">，</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">由于有着高额的进口关税</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">，实际上这些车都在中国制造</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">国家能源局官员</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">周喜安（译注：周为能源局综合司司长）上个月指出，</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">由于不断上升的汽车拥有量、</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">农业部门机械化提高带来的</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">柴油需求、</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">以及</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">观光客</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">为参加上海世博会引起</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">的</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">额外</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">航空煤油</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">消耗</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">，今年第二季度的石<span><span style=\"font-size:small\">化</span></span>燃料消耗很可能进一步增加</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">。</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">能源专家认为，中国</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">经济产出构成</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">的转变，会压倒其快速扩张的再生能源以及现有能源节约项目的夺人眼球的效果</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">。</span></span><br /><span style=\"font-size:small\"><br /></span></p>\n<div style=\"text-align:left\">\n<div style=\"text-align:left\"><img src=\"http://docs.google.com/File?id=dg5pc3d3_1495cr73qmgc_b\" style=\"height:732px;width:500px\"></div>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n<div style=\"margin:5pt 0pt\"><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">中国第一季度经济增长率为</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">12%</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">，而</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">同期石油和煤电消耗</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">的增长速度两倍于此，显示出</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">能源消耗增加不仅是经济复苏的结果，也是</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">工业活动构成变动的结果。</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">这一转</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">变部分归因于中国的经济刺激项目导致了</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">公共</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">建设工程</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">激增，</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">并进而引起对钢铁和水泥的需求。</span></span></div>\n<p><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">燃烧石</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">化</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">燃料释放出的二氧化碳被很多科学家</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">认为是</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">导致</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">气候变化</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">的</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">最</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">主要</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">的人为因素。</span></span></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://topics.nytimes.com/top/reference/timestopics/people/h/hu_jintao/index.html?inline=nyt-per\"><span><span style=\"color:blue\"><u><span style=\"font-size:small\">胡锦涛</span></u></span></span></a><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">主席去年</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">11</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">月许诺</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">，</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">到</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">2020</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">年，</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">中国政府将</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">大幅提高能效来降低温室气体</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">排放。</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">在</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">参加</span></span><a href=\"http://topics.nytimes.com/topics/reference/timestopics/subjects/u/united_nations_framework_convention_on_climate_change/index.html?inline=nyt-classifier\"><span><span style=\"color:blue\"><u><span style=\"font-size:small\">哥本哈根气候会议</span></u></span></span></a><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">三周后，温家宝总理反对任何针对</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">中国能效行为进行的</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">国际监测，或者是对总体<span><span style=\"font-size:small\">中国</span></span>能源消耗的强制性限制。</span></span></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://graphics8.nytimes.com/images/2010/05/07/business/07energy_CA2/07energy_CA2-articleInline.jpg\" style=\"float:left;height:249px;margin-left:0pt;margin-right:1em;width:190px\"><b><span style=\"font-size:x-small\">摄影：Sheng Li/路透社<br />图：工人们在安装电线。中国的目标是要将能源利用率提升20%</span></b></p>\n<p><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">中国目前的五年计划</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">（</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">2006-</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">2010</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">）已经设定了一个能效目标，但</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">现在</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">看起来不太可能</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">实现</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">。</span></span><br /><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">这个计划要求，截止到</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">2010</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">年，单位经济产出的能耗在</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">2005</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">年的基础上要下降</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">20%</span></span>。</p>\n<p><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">有那么一段时期，中国看起来正在朝这个目标迈进。根据</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">工业与信息化部</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">的数据，</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">2005</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">年至</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">2009</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">年间，</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">能效实际提高了超过</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">14%</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">。</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">但工信部在周四指出，</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">2010</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">年第一季度能效降低了</span></span><span style=\"font-size:small\">3.2%</span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">。</span></span>温总理说这一恶化会让中国要实现20%的目标变得“非常困难”。</p>\n<p><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">如果没有大的政策变动，比如提高燃料税，</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">“</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">他们不可能做到这一点</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">”</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">，苏格兰爱丁堡</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">麦肯兹公</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">司</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">（</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">Wood Mackenzie</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">，一家大型能源咨询公司</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">）</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">的首席能源经济学家</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">Julie Beatty</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">认为。</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">胡锦涛主席去年</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">11</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">月允诺，截止到</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">2020</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">年，中国会将其经济能效</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">提升40%</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">到</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">45%</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">。工信部周四的声明没有提到胡主席的允诺是否仍然有可能实现。</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">中</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">国国家统计局已经启动了一项对全国</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">过去</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">10</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">年能源统计数据</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">的修订，</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">重新计算</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">那些在</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">其他国家</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">数据中</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">常见的</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">细节</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">，这将使能效</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">计算复杂化。西方的专家也期望这次</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">修订会</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">显示</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">，</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">与以前所认为的相比</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">，</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">中国</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">一直都使用着</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">更多的能源，并释放了更多</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">的</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">温室气体。</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">现在修订数据会冒些风险，其他国家将不信任修订结果，并要求对中国未来的承诺进行更多的国际监测。</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">例如如果国家统计局在修订中提高了</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">2005</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">年的数据，那中国似乎已经</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">在本年底达到了提升能效</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">20%</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">的目标。</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">迄今为止，中国最近热烈拥抱的可再生能源</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">在降低</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">燃烧化石燃料</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">带来的排放量增加这一点上，</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">没起到什么作用。</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">第一季度的风能与去年相比已经翻番，</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">因为中国已成为世界上最大的风力涡轮机制造和安装国。</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">但风力依然只占到中国</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">发电能力</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">的</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">2%</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">——</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">因为风并不是总是在刮，风能只占</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">实际</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">电力</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">产出的</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">1%</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">同时，第一季度燃料密集型的重工业</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">产出同比上升了</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">22%</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">，而轻工业增加了</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">14%</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">。</span></span></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://topics.nytimes.com/top/reference/timestopics/people/p/rajendra_k_pachauri/index.html?inline=nyt-per\"></a><a href=\"http://topics.nytimes.com/top/reference/timestopics/organizations/i/intergovernmental_panel_on_climate_change/index.html?inline=nyt-org\">政府间气候变化专门委员会</a>（IPCC, 一个<a href=\"http://topics.nytimes.com/top/reference/timestopics/organizations/u/united_nations/index.html?inline=nyt-org\">联合国</a>的研究单位）主席<a href=\"http://topics.nytimes.com/top/reference/timestopics/people/p/rajendra_k_pachauri/index.html?inline=nyt-per\">Rajendra K. Pachauri</a>在一份电子邮件中指出，他相信中国是严肃对待其排放问题的。<br /><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">“</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">中国社会日益</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">认识到，大力减少温室气体排放对中国</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">总体而言是</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">有益的。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">”</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">他在获知最近的中国能源统计数据后写道。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">“</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">这一点很重要</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">，</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">不仅因为全球性的原因</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">——</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">因为中国排放着最多的温室气体</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">——</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">也因为它的人均排放量</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">在</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">快速增加。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">”</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">某种程度上讲，中国现在的能源消耗，或许</span></span><span style=\"font-size:small\"><span>将</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">在今后能帮助</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">限制</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">它的全球温室</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">气体</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">排放</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">。</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">举例来说</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">，</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">劳伦斯</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">.</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">伯克利国家实验室</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">（</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">Lawrence Berkeley National Laboratory</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">，隶属于美国能源部</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">的顶尖科学与工程研究机构</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">，译注）</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">中国能源专家</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">David Fridley</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">声称，</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">为</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">修筑铁路，</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">中国去年消耗了两亿吨水泥，</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">但整个美国经济</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">体也</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">只用了</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">9300</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">万吨。尽管水泥生产增加了能源利用和全球变暖气体排放</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">，但也扩展了铁路系统，而在世界范围内铁路</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">都</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">属于能效最高的</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">运输方式</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">10</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">年前中国</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">80%</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">的煤炭运输依靠铁路，现在这一比例</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">下降到</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">55%</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">，</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">迫于铁路运力</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">不足</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">，许多煤炭用户只好</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">用卡车拉煤。</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">根据</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">Fridley</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">先生的说法，运载一吨煤行驶一</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">英里</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">，卡车需要</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">10</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">倍或者更多的燃料。</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">但</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">现在，</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">新的高速客运铁路</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">为旧有铁路运</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">送煤炭或</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">其他货物留下了空间，</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">这个</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">比例可能</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">开始调低</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">能源效率低下</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">的卡车运输</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;times new roman&#39;\"><span style=\"font-size:small\">Fridley</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">先生</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:small\">表示。</span></span></p>\n<p><b>相关阅读：</b></p>\n<p><b><span style=\"font-family:calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:xx-small\"><span><span>►</span></span></span></span><a href=\"http://docs.google.com/leaf?id=0AXC6I8b9sUt9ZGc1cGMzZDNfODg2Y2YzY2ZjaGI&amp;sort=name&amp;layout=list&amp;pid=0B3C6I8b9sUt9MzIyYmE4MjItNWJiMC00MDRiLWE0MjYtZjhhNjMxMDY5ZTE0&amp;cindex=3\" title=\"卢广的获奖图片系列：中国的环境污染\">卢广的获奖图片系列：中国的环境污染</a></b></p>\n<p><b><span style=\"font-family:calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:xx-small\"><span><span>►</span></span></span></span><a href=\"http://docs.google.com/leaf?id=0AXC6I8b9sUt9ZGc1cGMzZDNfMTI4MGY3NnMya2Rm&amp;sort=name&amp;layout=list&amp;pid=0B3C6I8b9sUt9MzIyYmE4MjItNWJiMC00MDRiLWE0MjYtZjhhNjMxMDY5ZTE0\">亚洲时报：中国最大的敌人——大自然</a><br /></b></p>\n<p><b><span style=\"font-family:calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:xx-small\"><span><span>►</span></span></span></span><a href=\"http://docs.google.com/leaf?id=0AXC6I8b9sUt9ZGc1cGMzZDNfMTAwM2R4OHJmNWRy&amp;sort=name&amp;layout=list&amp;pid=0B3C6I8b9sUt9MzIyYmE4MjItNWJiMC00MDRiLWE0MjYtZjhhNjMxMDY5ZTE0\" title=\"华盛顿邮报：随着经济的快速发展，中国面临严重缺水\">华盛顿邮报：随着经济的快速发展，中国面临严重缺水</a></b></p>\n<p><b><span style=\"font-family:calibri\"><span style=\"font-size:xx-small\"><span><span>►</span></span></span></span><a href=\"http://docs.google.com/leaf?id=0AXC6I8b9sUt9ZGc1cGMzZDNfMTM4M2RrdHJ0cWR2&amp;sort=name&amp;layout=list&amp;pid=0B3C6I8b9sUt9MzIyYmE4MjItNWJiMC00MDRiLWE0MjYtZjhhNjMxMDY5ZTE0&amp;cindex=2\" title=\"连线访谈朱棣文：想要解决全球变暖问题？中国是关键\">连线访谈朱棣文：想要解决全球变暖问题？中国是关键</a></b></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:x-small\"><br />来源说明：本文原文来自文中标明的出版公司，译文1.0版本来源译者团队。</p>\n<p>收录说明：本文已经收录到“译者文集”中，同时进入“</span><span style=\"font-size:x-small\">最新消息”、“</span><span style=\"font-size:x-small\">译者频道—时事评论”、</span><span style=\"font-size:x-small\">“纽约时报”、“译者leros”索引。</span></p>\n<div><i><span style=\"font-size:x-small\">本文版权属于原出版公司及作者所有。©译者遵守</span><a href=\"http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/2.5/cn/\" title=\"CC协议2.5\"><span style=\"font-size:x-small\">CC协议2.5</span></a><span style=\"font-size:x-small\">您可以自由复制、发行、展览、表演、放映、广播或通过信息网络传播，创作演绎本作品。惟须遵守下列条件：署名，非商业性使用，相同方式